     F** EDTR08  ***************************************
     F*  CLEAR ABAWP10 31 DAY TABLE                    *
     F*  J.WATANABE    2024.07.18                      *
     F*------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALLING SEQ.
     F*                    CALL 'EDTR08 '
     F*                    PARM           $NONY   4
     F*                    PARM           $YM     6
     F*                    PARM           $MHIN  20
     F*  IN  $NONY   4A DELIVERY CODE
     F*  IN  $YM     6A DATE YYYYMM (EX. 202407)
     F*  IN  $MHIN  20A USER PART#
     F**************************************************
     FABAWL14 UF  E           K        DISK
     I            DS
     I                                        1  20 K#MHIN
     I                                        1   5 K#MHN1
     I                                        6  10 K#MHN2
     I                                       11  15 K#MHN3
     I                                       16  20 K#MHN4
      *=========================
      * MAIN ROUTINE
      *=========================
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           $NONY   4
     C                     PARM           $YM     6
     C                     PARM           $MHIN  20
      *
     C           K#14      KLIST
